          "blocks": {
            "text_W6LPdV": {
              "type": "text",
              "name": "t:names.text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>We are a small team with eight dogs and nine cats between us. We did not set out to build a brand, we set out to fix something we deal with every day. Too many products, too much noise, and not enough that simply work, feel safe to use and hold up over time.<br/><br/>So TIKOCAT freshly dipped its paws as of 2026 and we made it for the people who already show up for their pets and love them unconditionally. They are not just pets, they’re family. Everything we make is designed to meet you and your pet where they are and make the next step clear. No overcomplicating, no second guessing, just products that do their job, fit into real routines, keep going and looks great too! We design with care in mind, especially for the pets who feel everything. Quiet enough to keep them calm. Gentle enough for sensitive dogs and safe to use around cats. Because how a product works matters but how it feels for your pet matters just as much.<br/><br/>Good pet care is not the most expensive or the most elaborate. It is the kind that works and saves time. The kind that becomes part of your life so naturally you do not have to think about it. Week after week, without the guesswork and without the guilt. That is what we are sharing, alongside the people who choose their pets every single day.</p>",
